external_knowledge:
Available apartments are the ones with the 'availability_status' equal to 'available'; 
The ranking of apartments is based on the count of user actions in descending order; 
Average rent is calculated by averaging the average of the minimum and maximum rent prices of apartments in each city.

sql:
SELECT apartment_number, availability_status, views
FROM apartments
ORDER BY views DESC;

SELECT apartment_number
FROM apartments
WHERE views = (SELECT MAX(views) FROM apartments);
